snippet.title: Best VGM 2310 - Magicians & Looters - The Valley
snippet.description:
OST: https://morgopolisstudios.bandcamp.com/album/magicians-looters-soundtrack

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC
Magicians & Looters (2014)
The Valley
Morgopolis Studios
